@Buzzec Hey there mate! Hope you had a great weekend  
I would like to confirm something  you mentioned during the last Brew:

You shared that the habs that we will receive for owning a land plot will ne the only source of habs we can use on Starbases. I can imagine the team may then want to sell more. So we will indeed not be able to craft habs ourselves (be it on the target Starbase directly, or elsewhere)?

I need 700 more crew but the idea of loading 700 crew into Starbased via ledger makes me want to claw my eyes out.  Is there any workarounds or plans to fix this?    Like... why do we need to sign anything with the Starbased wallet to IMPORT crew?
For example, If i bought a bunch of crew on a hot wallet and then assigned them to my Starbased profile, I could bypass needing to sign with my ledger.  This is very much preferable.    Or any other solution, I just can't bring myself to buy a meaningful amount of crew and if I'm not willing to do it... who is?

@Buzzec
